{"tid":773673,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"韓國學者：朝鮮古文明可追溯至5000年前　先於黃河文明","createTime":"2018-08-09T16:56:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-09T17:40:23.000Z","uid":182772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8b3163492fae2dfdbae160d2fc93c5f34411b5d7","tid":773673,"uid":182772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T16:56:04.000Z","msg":"《朝鮮日報》報道，首爾大學榮譽教授慎鏞廈（신용하）說：「古朝鮮文明在5000年前出現，是繼美索不達米亞文明和埃及文明之後的世界第三大古代文明。」<br />\n<br />\n慎鏞廈出版了《古朝鮮文明的社會史》一書，他的研究指出古朝鮮文明在公元前30世紀，起源於現時的朝鮮半島大同江流域和遼東地區。<br />\n<br />\n冰河時期結束之後古朝鮮半島出現了農耕文化，成功栽培稻和豆。在新石器時代，由於農業革命帶來更多人口，一部分人移居到北方地區，包括遼河以東及遼河以西地區，他們分別成為穢族與貊族。貊族在5000年前，因氣候異常現象持續，而向東南遷移，在大同江流域與韓族結合，成立了以青銅器文化為基礎的古朝鮮。<br />\n<br />\n報道引述慎鏞廈指，<span style=\"color: red;\">他認為西方文明起源自美索不達米亞文明、埃及文明，而相對的東方文明則是古朝鮮文明，而非黃河文明。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（朝鮮日報）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/即時國際/220802/韓國學者-朝鮮古文明可追溯至5000年前-先於黃河文明\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%2F220802%2F%E9%9F%93%E5%9C%8B%E5%AD%B8%E8%80%85-%E6%9C%9D%E9%AE%AE%E5%8F%A4%E6%96%87%E6%98%8E%E5%8F%AF%E8%BF%BD%E6%BA%AF%E8%87%B35000%E5%B9%B4%E5%89%8D-%E5%85%88%E6%96%BC%E9%BB%83%E6%B2%B3%E6%96%87%E6%98%8E&d=um9KhaGFcCcSmGPdFj9BVrIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=b1740d53\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/即時國際/220802/韓國學者-朝鮮古文明可追溯至5000年前-先於黃河文明</a>"},{"pid":"92160c0ba7fcfa284ec05ad830f540fbe3171f37","tid":773673,"uid":15362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T16:57:51.000Z","msg":"大家都是朝野人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e53f9cf08cfdfa1820696181448d5c19ae6cd437","tid":773673,"uid":15362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"92160c0ba7fcfa284ec05ad830f540fbe3171f37","tid":773673,"uid":15362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T16:57:51.000Z","msg":"大家都是朝野人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T16:58:06.000Z","msg":"鮮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a46c85533edc3e50edfbd011d64b9cd19a2b36e","tid":773673,"uid":90820,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T17:00:28.000Z","msg":"端午節係韓國嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f65b3e7f61b244e3e6d0a6a99934285d9541e1cb","tid":773673,"uid":149089,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T17:19:14.000Z","msg":"原文個記者都係到串個教授發up瘋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n連韓國網民都係到講&quot;我們國家的起源有咁不堪到要拎人地果啲咩?&quot;<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n泡菜又要柒出國際<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ec6edb026c300cee32ebfd55c82f00867adfbbb","tid":773673,"uid":2507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T17:40:23.000Z","msg":"南泡又真係幾鐘意衝出嚟柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}